  "text": "H. pylori infection was diagnosed upon a positive result in the rapid urease test and 13 C-UBT. The successful eradication of H. pylori was defined as a decrease to <4\u2030 in the [CITATION_1] C-UBT. Also, H. pylori infection density was quantified indirectly by a [CITATION_2] C-UBT and measurement of the ammonia concentration in gastric juice aspirate. 21 ",
